instructions: Put the dinner fork on the bottom left side of the table cloth
Put the dinner knife on the bottom right side of the table cloth
Put the salad fork  to left of the dinner fork on the table cloth
Put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife on the table cloth
Put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife on the tablecloth
Put the dessert spoon on the top center area of the tablecloth
Put the dessert spoon to the right of the soup spoon on the table cloth
Put the dessert spoon in the top center area of the tablecloth
Put the dinner plate between the dinner fork and dinner knife under the dessert spoon
Put the bread plate to the direct left of the dessert spoon
Put the the butter knife on the top corner of the bread plate with it's tip pointing diagonally left
Put the wine glass right above the spoon spoon
Put the water glass to the upper left of the wine glass above the dinner plate
Put the napkin in the center of the dinner plate
